snippet.textDisplay:
CONGRATULATIONS, MARCELITO‼️😃👍🏼🍾🥂

I have an idea for the finals. Please hear me out on this! Simon says you are to take a high risk. What if you sing DESPACITO! Bring that really fiesta party mood with dancers and bring the whole audience and judges for that dance mood!
I saw your DESPACITO video in Dubai and I thought this would be a TURN AROUND CHANGE! The whole audience and judges would not expect this sudden transition from Opera songs to this Party/Dance /Pop side of you. Making you a versatile all around singer! From my observation looking at X-Factor and AGT or BGT, audiences and judges love to bring that Party Fiesta mood (look at Hans who was able to go to the Finals because of that lively performance) only that reason why he got through because of the party mood and gave the show and audiences pure lively entertainment.
You can also do this, Marcelito! You sang DESPACITO so perfectly as you brought up that performer and entertainer inside of you. Bring that out and SURPRICE the AUDIENCES, JUDGES and SIMON! I bet my soul that this is the PERFECT RISK that will give you the BIG WIN from the Judges, the Audience and THE CHAMPIONS TITLE! Everyone knows you can sing Dual Voices. Now let them hear MARCELITO POMOY the Performer. And Simon will see you can sing anything and may get you for a record deal and possibly a contract for his own company (like Susan Boyle, Paul Potts and One Direction). Please consider this. This will be a great big BANG that will blow the roof off the stage. (look at the video of Fourth Impact in X-Factor Audition when the girls took the whole audience and judges to their feet and blew the roof off of Wembley Stadium). Think about this, Marcelito.
I am rooting for you for THE WIN‼️
